name: Nudie Jeans Ecru Embro Thin Finn Slim Fit Jeans in Organic Dry
description:
• Men's skinny low yoke jeans by Nudie
  • Contrast top stitching and embroidered pockets
  • Italian 10.75oz dry cotton and dark wash
additionalInfo:
98% Cotton, 2% Elastane
Made in Italy

Nudie are a true and passionate jeans brand that are not looking for short -term trends but a collection that is strong long-lasting and durable 
Design goes beyond creating just a product that serves to fulfill a need or a function. Nudie Jeans age beautifully with colour that fades and gives the denim its character
careInfo: 30 degree machine wash, do not bleach, cool iron, do not tumble dry, do not dry clean
